{
  "stem": "888.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes they would give you, like, a piece of margarine with it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or, they would give you a little of-- they called-- what they called marmalade.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And water, of course, I don't even recall, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, from our camp, I suppose it was 700, around like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, because like I mentioned, you know, that people died away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Constantly died away from-- you know, there was elderly people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, elderly people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could imagine a man of 40, 40, 45, you understand, who hasn't eaten-- you know, I mean, they, they needed food more than even us children.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they worked and marched and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, they needed more food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they, they, they-- day by day, you know, they dropped weight.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they became like, like, what we called Muselmann-- you know, like for instance, starved people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, like skin and bone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, and they, they just fell away by the wayside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, every, every day, there were people taken away, you know, died.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes, you know, they had a, like a-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't call it a hospital, but a place, you know, where there was an office over there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they might have-- we had a suspicion, you know, that they might have given them, you know, an injection, and away-- put them away.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Approximately 600, 700 people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you can't-- really, I can't estimate, like I said, because then when we came into the camp, there was other people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sure there must have been about 100, 150 people, you know, killed on the road, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that depends.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
